{"tid":148030,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"漫威《異人族》開拍  黑蝠王亮相輕輕一哼撕裂宇宙","createTime":"2017-03-08T09:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T10:18:50.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5b0cb72e33ca57ef7f03225416dfabd8615956","tid":148030,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"漫威與ABC聯合打造的超級英雄電影《異人族》電視劇版日前公佈首批夏威夷拍攝片場照，安松&middot;蒙特扮演的異人族大哥&ldquo;黑蝠王&rdquo;亮相，他的能力非常強悍，輕輕一哼就相當於引爆一顆核武器般毀天滅地，甚至可以撕裂宇宙空間，所以他基本上不說話保持沉默，而且佩帶的天線可以抑制能力以防傷害朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AP7xv32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAP7xv32.jpg&h=8fd1a4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;黑蝠王&rdquo;造型，雖然很酷但和原著不太一樣，不過可能只是眾多服裝的其中一種<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Er251cQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEr251cQ.jpg&h=90700c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，片場還出現了&ldquo;異人族&rdquo;水晶的重達2000磅萌寵&ldquo;破傷風&rdquo;，其裝配的道具可以傳送&ldquo;破傷風&rdquo;以及其他角色，還包括超強的咬力，片場模型非常巨大，後期轉為CG特效。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Af8czB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Af8czB.jpg&h=625f092d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nyvUGc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nyvUGc.jpg&h=1ea381cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;破傷風&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　《異人族》主演陣容還包括賽琳達&middot;斯萬扮演的&ldquo;黑蝠王&rdquo;妻子&ldquo;美杜莎&rdquo;，可以任意控制髮型的增長，隨意操控。《權力的遊戲》伊万&middot;瑞恩扮演的&ldquo;黑蝠王&rdquo;弟弟馬克西穆斯，智慧、創造力超群，還包括心靈感應與控制。Ken Leung扮演的&ldquo;黑蝠王&rdquo;表兄卡爾納克，可以感知缺陷，身體能力超越美國隊長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9cHTYo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9cHTYo.jpg&h=5b994d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑蝠王、美杜莎、馬克西穆斯<br />\n<br />\n　　其他角色還包括Eme Ikwuako扮演戈爾工，體能超群，可以製造地震波。《街霸》演員Mike Moh扮演崔坦，適宜水體戰鬥。Isabelle Cornish扮演水晶，可以激活並操控四大元素地、水、火、氣。Sonya Balmores扮演Auran，&ldquo;異人族&rdquo;護衛隊隊長，嚴肅輔佐阿提蘭的王。Ellen Woglom扮演未公開名字的角色，設定為是個聰明﹑熱情﹑專注，甚至會專注到忘了社交技巧；她過去都把生活奉獻給一家私人航空公司，僅次於對太空的熱忱。她將準備捲入冒險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y47f3kZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY47f3kZ.jpg&h=5ae74d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水晶、戈爾工、崔坦、Auran<br />\n<br />\n　　漫威《異人族》電視劇第一與第二集採用IMAX攝影機拍攝，2017年9月登陸全球IMAX影院，ABC電視台兩週後播放傳統電視劇版，第一季八集，漫威還將打造《異人族》電影版，但因為《蜘蛛俠：返校季》的加入，《異人族》延期與《蟻人和黃蜂》同檔期上映，然後被擱置。<br />\n本文由遊民星空製作發布，轉載請註明出處。"},{"pid":"a8c3a10eac55eae5d04d99dd2624b230c15b7e28","tid":148030,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"之前又話唔拍異人族,E家又拍,好難捉摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ba81f8c9a087f21af6f11a60169b25dcda7d1f","tid":148030,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"係咪即係電視劇aos入面daisy d 族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b250f6dc7b0792cb188d16663c2f159ceeccfd4","tid":148030,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪即係電視劇aos入面daisy d 族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"b46d137edead0ca9741a1ba18825ba2c5665702e","tid":148030,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前又話唔拍異人族,E家又拍,好難捉摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話唔拍，係無限期押後電影"},{"pid":"a50d87c15324c79bd3d0632afe36e143ce7d38f7","tid":148030,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪即係電視劇aos入面daisy d 族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n原來班半外星人咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766a7a0b04d724a8178281195f5435002092574c","tid":148030,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪即係電視劇aos入面daisy d 族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n原來班半外星人咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電視劇畢直低電影好多<br />\n出啲太勁嘅人無咁多錢做CG<br />\n我估呢套啲人嘅能力都會被削弱"},{"pid":"04eb77676c6a7886479af326a72c8f4aaad9738e","tid":148030,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"對inhuman 反感到一個點"},{"pid":"91c514cbc198ed5b20f2f63618690d5c0f644d66","tid":148030,"uid":25112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"又拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f326ea57de9c60266f80ef3a03221b0f660866e8","tid":148030,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對inhuman 反感到一個點</blockquote><br />\nInhumans不知幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94afd2f3233f21df3597e9a72d36556969b2dcc0","tid":148030,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對inhuman 反感到一個點</blockquote><br />\nInhumans不知幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班人都無咩野問題，但係marvel夾鳩硬推inhuman 反效果"},{"pid":"3a1214993a69452d21beb8e1e0de55f01d6d90dd","tid":148030,"uid":22240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"電視劇版？不了"},{"pid":"7838fa51540a892cab0ef37292a893cc8dc92675","tid":148030,"uid":60023,